<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

        <div id="displaybox" class="text-center">
            <div id="introtext">
                <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 12px;">Powered by <a href="https://www.openuv.io/dashboard" target="_blank">Open UV</a></p>
                <h1>Sunscreen Advisor</h1>
                    <p>Planning to go outside?</p>
                    <p>Wait!</p>
                    <p>As the US Environmental Protection Agency says, when the <a href="https://www.epa.gov/sunsafety/uv-index-scale-0" target="_blank">UV index</a> value is 3 or higher, protection like sunscreen is needed.</p>
                    <p>Input your Latitude and Longitude from <a href="https://www.google.com/maps" target="_blank">Google Maps</a> (Right Click your Location)</p>
                    <p>and press the button below and see UV value</p>
                    <form action="/" id="form" class="form" method="POST">
                        <label for="lat">Enter your Latitude</label>
                        <input type="text" id="lat" name="lat" placeholder="123.45" class="form-control">

                        <label for="lng">Enter your Longitude</label>
                        <input type="text" id="lng" name="lng" placeholder="123.45" class="form-control">
                        
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Today's Index</button>
                    </form>
