                            <p>Low UV light detected, no protection needed.</p>
                        <% } else if (valueRound >= 3 && valueRound <= 7) { %>
                            <p>Index Value: <%= value %> ‚òÄÔ∏è</p>
                            <p>Moderate UV light detected, protection needed.</p>
                            <p>Sunscreen and protective clothing suggested.</p>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <p>Index Value: <%= value %> üî•</p>
                            <p>High UV light detected, extra protection needed.</p>
